Ranks
---------------------------------------------
Guide   - can transport to newbie area (and back to where they were?)
        - allows lower level characters to follow (but not group)
        - can summon helper spirit to newbie location????
Caretaker all of the above plus:
        - can transport to any location/character
        - can reset rooms/ reload mobs/objects
        - can purge mobs/objects
        - can create home rooms for characters
Overseer all of the above plus:
        - can change sex/race/stats/xp/gold of players
        - can load in new areas/mob/object files and reboot game
        - can change idle times and set nodelete on pfiles
        - can punish players who are repeatedly offensive (how?)
        - can code new commands/skills/spells/music
        - can summon players (no mana needed)
GOD      all of the above plus:
        - unlimmited access to SMUD code base
        - can promote players
        - anything else????                                                     

